OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry today, chance of an
OL,6,Fisolated shower this morning. Rather
OL,7,Fcloudy but some bright or sunny spells
OL,8,Fbreaking through this afternoon.
OL,9,FPleasantly warm in any sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness. Rain will spread
OL,13,Facross western areas during the early
OL,14,Fhours, but remaining dry across the
OL,15,Feast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FRain spreading east through
OL,18,Fthe morning. Drier with bright spells
OL,19,Fin the afternoon along with a few
OL,20,Fshowers, these turning heavy in the
OL,21,Fwest later. Colder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
