OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome sunshine on Friday, outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spreading northeast in the
OL,8,Fevening. Mainly dry on Saturday.
OL,9,FBreezy with showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
